                                                    </tr>
                                                    <tr>
                                                        <td>Advertising</td>
                                                        <td>Intended to make advertising more relevant to users and more valuable to advertisers. For example, we may use Cookies to serve you interest-based ads, such as ads that are displayed to you based on your visits to other websites, or to tell us if you have recently interacted with an ad.</td>
                                                    </tr>
                                                    <tr>
                                                        <td>Analytics</td>
